# Approach
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->
We are creating Set that will contain all vowel letters. Go through k first letters and update count if it's needed. Than by using sliding windows technique we are getting right answer. Adventages of this solution is that we can easily update vowels set(adding uppercase vowel letters) by not affecting the main code. This solution is more generic.
